                                         CAPE TOWN - Murder accused Henri van Breda is on the witness stand for a second day. He’s accused of murdering his parents and brother, and attempting to kill his sister at their family home in 2015. He maintains his innocence, claiming that an intruder is to blame for the murders. WATCH: Henri van Breda's testimony courtesy of News24 